<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038384" n="143r"/>
<p>
               <lb/>Gratum mihi fuit intelligere ex ultima Tua <rs key="B_1717-11-11_991170517038405501" type="letter">epistola</rs> <add>ante octiduum scripta</add> quod transmissum <rs key="biblio_KGKQAP5S biblio_8JCIWHQ6 biblio_RC6TN74M" type="biblios">fasciculum</rs>
<lb/>acceperis; multo autem gratius fuit audire, Te fortasse Cathedram Medicin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Practic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
               <lb/>primariam accepturum esse. Utinam in hac persistas sententia, et <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> Re<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>formatores hanc Cathedram Tibi deferant, sic enim dabitur occasio, amicitia Tua
               <lb/>cum fructu et <subst><del>utilitate</del><add>jucunditate</add></subst> coram utendi. Quod ad me attinet, certus sis, oro, me omnia
               <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi hac de re confidere voluisti, silentio tecturum esse, ne illi quos <subst><del><gap/></del><add>putas</add></subst>
<lb/>quicquam subolfaciant. <abbr>Ill.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> Marchio <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Poleni</rs> <del>se nihil </del>promisit, se nihil eo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum neglecturum esse, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in Tui favorem facere poterit, cujus rei sine dubio
               <lb/>ab ipsomet jam certior factus <subst><del>eris</del><add>fuisti</add></subst>. Gratias Tibi ago pro eo, quod mihi offeras, Te
               <lb/>posthac <rs key="B_1717-11-12_991170517038205501 B_1717-11-08_991170517038705501" type="letters">literas</rs> meas in <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Patriam</rs> destinatas, si velim, per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs> missurum esse.
               <lb/>Ego illas hucusque per <rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">Bergomum</rs> misi, quia expertus sum, eas sic breviori tem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>poris spatio, quam si per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs> eant, <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs> venire; sed quoniam episto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad me <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basilea</rs> <add>per eandem viam</add> transmiss<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> diutius in itinere morantur, tentabo num<del> sper</del>
<lb/>si per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs> mittantur citius huc veniant, adeoque mandabo, ut illas posthac ad Te
               <lb/>mittant, sumta ad id occasione quando <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> meus ad Te scribet. Eidem <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> meo
               <lb/><date>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terita die Sabbati</date> omnia perscripsi, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <subst><del><gap/></del><add>jussisti</add></subst> ratione expensarum pro litteris
               <lb/>Tuis. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum Te rogo, ut quando mihi respondere voles, mihi simul significes, an
               <lb/>ultima Tua <rs key="B_1717-11-11_991170517038405501" type="letter">epistola</rs> illi, quam ad <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Polenum</rs> dedisti, inclusa fuerit necne. In<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>terim 
            </p>
<closer>vale et mihi favere perge. <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <date when="1717-11-19"><abbr>d.</abbr> 19. <abbr>Nov.<hi rend="sup">bris</hi></abbr> 1717</date></dateline>.</closer>
</div>
